dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Wayne Walker. May I have your name, please?
Hi, Wayne. My name is Christina Morris.
Nice to meet you, Christina. Can you please provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is one two three four five and my date of birth is zero seven dash eight two dash one nine eight zero.
Thank you, Christina. One last thing, what is the make and model of your vehicle that's listed on your policy?
Great, thank you for that information. Is there anything specific you'd like to discuss today, Christina?
I wanted to inquire about roadside assistance coverage on my policy.
Sure thing, Christina. Let me provide you with details on the roadside assistance coverage you have. Thank you for reaching out.
If you have any other questions in the future, feel free to contact us. Have a great day, Christina!
Thank you, Wayne. You too, have a great day.
